description: FHIR Value set/code system definition for HL7 v2 table 0616 ( Address Expiration Reason)
name: v2 Address Expiration Reason

text.div:
Address Expiration Reason

CodeDescriptionCommentVersion
C CorrectedThe address has been replaced with a corrected versionadded v2.6
E Added in errorThe address was incorrect and should never have been associated with the individualadded v2.6
M MovedThe individual associated with the address has moved and is no longer reachable at the addressadded v2.6
R On requestThe associated individual requested that the address be removed from their recordadded v2.6
